,"c":"تَوَكَّلْنَا","d":"twَkَlَّnْāَ","e":"tawakkalnā"},{"b":"54.8","h":"77.29","c":"وَإِلَيْكَ","d":"wʾَilِyَkَْ","e":"wa-ilayka"},{"b":"55.","h":"78.44","c":"أَنَبْنَا","d":"ʾanَbَnْāَ","e":"anabnā"},{"b":"56.7","h":"79.69","c":"وَإِلَيْكَ","d":"wʾَilِyَkَْ","e":"wa-ilayka"},{"b":"57.6","h":"80.83","c":"الْمَصِيرُ","d":"lٱmْṣَyِrُ","e":"l-maṣīru"}],"a":{"g":"There has already been for you an excellent pattern in Abraham and those with him, when they said to their people, \"Indeed, we are disassociated from you and from whatever you worship other than Allah. We have denied you, and there has appeared between us and you animosity and hatred forever until you believe in Allah alone\" except for the saying of Abraham to his father, \"I will surely ask forgiveness for you, but I have not [power to do] for you anything against Allah. Our Lord, upon You we have relied, and to You we have returned, and to You is the destination.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ربنا عليك توكلنا وإليك أنبنا وإليك المصير\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, our Lord [Rabbana], upon You we have placed our trust [tawakkalna], and to You we have turned in repentance [anabna], and to You is the final destination [al-maseer].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.17","h":"0.3","c":"رَبَّنَا","d":"rbَnَّāَ","e":"rabbanā"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.38","c":"لَا","d":"lāَ","e":"lā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"1.74","c":"تَجْعَلْنَا","d":"tgَjعْʿlَnْāَ","e":"tajʿalnā"},{"b":"2.6","h":"3.24","c":"فِتْنَةً","d":"ftِnْẗًَ","e":"fit'natan"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.25","c":"لِلَّذِينَ","d":"llِّdَّhyِnَ","e":"lilladhīna"},{"b":"4.7","h":"5.7","c":"كَفَرُوا","d":"kfَrَwُā۟","e":"kafarū"},{"b":"5.5","h":"6.84","c":"وَاغْفِرْ","d":"wغٱَfْrِْ","e":"wa-igh'fir"},{"b":"6.2","h":"7.55","c":"لَنَا","d":"lnَāَ","e":"lanā"},{"b":"6.8","h":"8.42","c":"رَبَّنَا","d":"rbَnَّāَٓ","e":"rabbanā"},{"b":"8.2","h":"10.99","c":"إِنَّكَ","d":"ʾinِkََّ","e":"innaka"},{"b":"9.8","h":"12.27","c":"أَنْتَ","d":"ʾanَtَ","e":"anta"},{"b":"11.2","h":"13.51","c":"الْعَزِيزُ","d":"lٱعْʿzَyِzُ","e":"l-ʿazīzu"},{"b":"12.4","h":"14.8","c":"الْحَكِيمُ","d":"lٱḥْkَyِmُ","e":"l-ḥakīmu"}],"a":{"g":"Our Lord, make us not [objects of] torment for the disbelievers and forgive us, our Lord. Indeed, it is You who is the Exalted in Might, the Wise.\""}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.09","h":"0.5","c":"لَقَدْ","d":"lqَdَْ","e":"laqad"},{"b":"0.59","h":"1.01","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.76","c":"لَكُمْ","d":"lkَmُْ","e":"lakum"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.38","c":"فِيهِمْ","d":"fyِhmِْ","e":"fīhim"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.36","c":"أُسْوَةٌ","d":"ʾasُwْẗٌَ","e":"us'watun"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.4","c":"حَسَنَةٌ","d":"ḥsَnَẗٌَ","e":"ḥasanatun"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.49","c":"لِمَنْ","d":"lmِّnَ","e":"liman"},{"b":"5.5","h":"6.76","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"6.1","h":"7.58","c":"يَرْجُوا","d":"yrَgْjwُā۟","e":"yarjū"},{"b":"7.0","h":"8.37","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"lٱlhََّ","e":"l-laha"},{"b":"7.5","h":"9.27","c":"وَالْيَوْمَ","d":"wlٱَyْwَmَْ","e":"wal-yawma"},{"b":"8.4","h":"10.47","c":"الْءَاخِرَ","d":"lٱءْāَkhrَِ","e":"l-ākhira"},{"b":"9.9","h":"13","c":"وَمَنْ","d":"wmَnَ","e":"waman"},{"b":"11.","h":"14.12","c":"يَتَوَلَّ","d":"ytَwَlََّ","e":"yatawalla"},{"b":"11.9","h":"15.15","c":"فَإِنَّ","d":"fʾَinَِّ","e":"fa-inna"},{"b":"13.1","h":"16.59","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"lٱlhََّ","e":"l-laha"},{"b":"13.9","h":"17.42","c":"هُوَ","d":"hwَُ","e":"huwa"},{"b":"14.3","h":"17.89","c":"الْغَنِيُّ","d":"lٱغْnَàُِّ","e":"l-ghaniyu"},{"b":"15.2","h":"19.02","c":"الْحَمِيدُ","d":"lٱḥْmَyِdُ","e":"l-ḥamīdu"}],"a":{"g":"There has certainly been for you in them an excellent pattern for anyone whose hope is in Allah and the Last Day. And whoever turns away - then indeed, Allah is the Free of need, the Praiseworthy."}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.04","c":"عَسَى","d":"عʿsَàَ","e":"ʿasā"},{"b":"0.58","h":"0.44","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"lٱlhَُّ","e":"l-lahu"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.38","c":"أَنْ","d":"ʾanَ","e":"an"},{"b":"2.4","h":"2.48","c":"يَجْعَلَ","d":"ygَjعْʿlََ","e":"yajʿala"},{"b":"2.9","h":"3.09","c":"بَيْنَكُمْ","d":"byَnْkَmُْ","e":"baynakum"},{"b":"3.9","h":"4.2","c":"وَبَيْنَ","d":"wbَyَnَْ","e":"wabayna"},{"b":"4.7","h":"5.1","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"lٱdَّhyِnَ","e":"alladhīna"},{"b":"5.6","h":"6.13","c":"عَادَيْتُمْ","d":"عʿāَdyَtْmُ","e":"ʿādaytum"},{"b":"6.5","h":"8.29","c":"مِنْهُمْ","d":"mnِّhْmُ","e":"min'hum"},{"b":"9.1","h":"9.75","c":"مَوَدَّةً","d":"mwَّdَẗًَّ","e":"mawaddatan"},{"b":"10.5","h":"12.55","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wlٱَlhَُّ","e":"wal-lahu"},{"b":"11.4","h":"13.66","c":"قَدِيرٌ","d":"qdَyِrٌ","e":"qadīrun"},{"b":"13.9","h":"16.7","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wlٱَlhَُّ","e":"wal-lahu"},{"b":"14.8","h":"17.83","c":"غَفُورٌ","d":"غfَwُrٌ","e":"ghafūrun"},{"b":"15.9","h":"18.85","c":"رَحِيمٌ","d":"rḥَّyِmٌ","e":"raḥīmun"}],"a":{"g":"Perhaps Allah will put, between you and those to whom you have been enemies among them, affection. And Allah is competent, and Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وينبغي أن لا يبالغ في البغضة عند الوقيعة قال الله تعالى عسى الله أن يجعل بينكم وبين الذين عاديتم منهم مودة\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, it is not fitting to be excessive in hatred [baghd] at the moment of injury [waqi'a]. Allah, the Exalted, has said: \"Perhaps Allah will bring about affection [mawadda] between you and those you have considered enemies among them.\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.26","c":"لَا","d":"lāَّ","e":"lā"},{"b":"0.51","h":"0.7","c":"يَنْهَاكُمُ","d":"ynَhْàَkٰmُُ","e":"yanhākumu"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.14","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"lٱlhَُّ","e":"l-lahu"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.87","c":"عَنِ","d":"عʿnَِ","e":"ʿani"},{"b":"2.8","h":"3.34","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"lٱdَّhyِnَ","e":"alladhīna"},{"b":"3.8","h":"4.43","c":"لَمْ","d":"lmَْ","e":"lam"},{"b":"4.1","h":"4.7","c":"يُقَاتِلُوكُمْ","d":"yqُtَٰlِwُkmُْ","e":"yuqātilūkum"},{"b":"5.7","h":"6.63","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"6","h":"6.98","c":"الدِّينِ","d":"lٱdyِّnِ","e":"l-dīni"},{"b":"6.7","h":"7.9","c":"وَلَمْ","d":"wlَmَْ","e":"walam"},{"b":"7.3","h":"8.39","c":"يُخْرِجُوكُمْ","d":"ykُhrْgِjwُkmُ","e":"yukh'rijūkum"},{"b":"9.8","h":"10.6","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِّ","e":"min"},{"b":"10.6","h":"11.42","c":"دِيَارِكُمْ","d":"dyِrَٰkِmُْ","e":"diyārikum"},{"b":"11.7","h":"12.78","c":"أَنْ","d":"ʾanَ","e":"an"},{"b":"12.8","h":"13.61","c":"تَبَرُّوهُمْ","d":"tbَrَwُّhmُْ","e":"tabarrūhum"},{"b":"14.2","h":"15.29","c":"وَتُقْسِطُوا","d":"wtَqُsْṭِwُāٓ۟","e":"watuq'siṭū"},{"b":"16.7","h":"17.89","c":"إِلَيْهِمْ","d":"ʾilِyَhْmِْ","e":"ilayhim"},{"b":"18.1","h":"20.85","c":"إِنَّ","d":"ʾinَِّ","e":"inna"},{"b":"19.4","h":"21.99","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"lٱlhََّ","e":"l-laha"},{"b":"20.2","h":"22.85","c":"يُحِبُّ","d":"yḥُbُِّ","e":"yuḥibbu"},{"b":"21.0","h":"23.83","c":"الْمُقْسِطِينَ","d":"lٱmْqُsْṭِyِnَ","e":"l-muq'siṭīna"}],"a":{"g":"Allah does not forbid you from those who do not fight you because of religion and do not expel you from your homes - from being righteous toward them a